{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readonly","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"reuseIdentifier","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You specify the reuse identifier when you create the view. You use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"identifier later to retrieve an annotation view that was created previously but"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which is currently unused because its annotation is not on-screen."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you define distinctly different types of annotations (with distinctly"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"different annotation views to go with them), you can differentiate between the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation types by specifying different reuse identifiers for each one."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/reuseidentifier"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)reuseIdentifier","symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"reuseIdentifier","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"reuseIdentifier","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"reuseIdentifier","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L139","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"}},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/reuseIdentifier"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string that identifies that this annotation view is reusable."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotationView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/reuseIdentifier":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"reuseIdentifier","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/reuseIdentifier","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/reuseidentifier","title":"reuseIdentifier","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string that identifies that this annotation view is reusable."}]}}}